modName: Piercing and cuff pack for Skyrim
summary:
Slave armor, three sort of labia piercings, belly piercing, nipple chain or just rings.
Slave collar and ankle cuffs.
descriptionHtml:
Three sort of labia piercings, belly piercing, nipple chain or just rings.
Slave collar and ankle cuffs.
The slave armor who Lydia is wearing, it increase her brest size a litle :o)
All craftable however still not safe for work.

You can wear one of the labia piercings, the belly piercing and the nipple chain or rings at once. 
All piercings can be enchanted as rings.

Slave collar can be worn with amulet. 
The ankle cuffs can not be worn with boots, they clip to much.

The niple chains and  is for CBBE slim, 
an optional set for the huge breasts in the slave armor is under large breast replacer, you can only have one set.

Technical:
Labia piercings, uses slot 58, belly uses 57 and nipple 56. 
The neck collar uses slot 45. 

Credit Jammer who made all the meshes and the slave armor.

No comment because of an bug at nexus
author: Zaria
